{"tid":812991,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓爆2018】荃灣中心兩房減價45萬沽 5年微升74%","createTime":"2018-09-10T05:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T05:55:56.000Z","uid":43146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d9d48f6d93d98c6ed0eb9c3fd284df4fc8979547","tid":812991,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:49:28.000Z","msg":"各區二手屋苑均出現跌價成交，但普遍減價10%內均見承接。<br />\n<br />\n美聯物業鍾家豪表示，荃灣中心昆明樓15座中層G室，兩房間隔，實用面積374方呎，放盤約兩個月，叫價580萬元，剛減價45萬至535萬元售出，呎價14,305元，比高位平約3%。賣方2013年2月以308萬元買入，賬面獲利227萬元或74%。<br />\n<br />\n記者:朱連峰"},{"pid":"b04167b00ccd95086b945c93c940630641e7e304","tid":812991,"uid":43146,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"標題打錯，應該係：荃灣中心兩房業主直劈45萬含淚求售，微賺74%<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}